OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F354A1774213555
OL,3,CCouncil admits inability to safety
OL,4,Ccheck 1,500 bridges
OL,6,FCouncil chiefs have revealed their
OL,7,Fstruggle to conduct structural and
OL,8,Fsafety compliance checks for the 1,500
OL,9,Fbridges in their area.
OL,11,FDumfries and Galloway Council admitted
OL,12,Fthat it cannot verify the structural
OL,13,Fintegrity or safety of all of the
OL,14,Fbridges, claiming that staff shortages
OL,15,Fand the Covid pandemic have caused a
OL,16,Fbacklog of inspections.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G1/5
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
