CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F354A1774213555
OL,3,CCouncil admits inability to safety
OL,4,Ccheck 1,500 bridges
OL,6,FThe revelation came almost a year
OL,7,Fsince the sudden closure of
OL,8,FKirkcudbright Bridge, when engineers
OL,9,Fdiscovered structural issues.
OL,10,FKirkcudbright Bridge currently
OL,11,Foperates with traffic restrictions,
OL,12,Fand needs to be replaced.
OL,14,FA council report said that this
OL,15,Fclosure "consumed the majority of the
OL,16,FBridges and Structures Team" and led
OL,17,Fto the backlog.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/5
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,355,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F354A1774213555
OL,3,CCouncil admits inability to safety
OL,4,Ccheck 1,500 bridges
OL,6,FThe number of staff in the bridges
OL,7,Fteam has also dropped from 15 to 10,
OL,8,Fleading to what the council described
OL,9,Fas "significant pressure and reduction
OL,10,Fof capacity".
OL,12,FAs of November 2025, 73% of the
OL,13,Fplanned general and principle bridge
OL,14,Finspections had been completed by the
OL,15,Fcouncil.
OL,17,FThe local authority hopes the backlog
OL,18,Fwill be cleared during 2026-27.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/5
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
