CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F354A1774213555
OL,3,CCouncil admits inability to safety
OL,4,Ccheck 1,500 bridges
OL,6,FNearly 1,400 of Dumfries and
OL,7,FGalloway's bridges cross over
OL,8,Fwaterways, and the majority of them
OL,9,Fare of masonry arch design.
OL,11,FA report, due to be presented to
OL,12,Fcouncillors on Tuesday March 24, says:
OL,13,F"The Bridges and Structures Team, like
OL,14,Fmany other teams across other local
OL,15,Fauthorities, are facing significant
OL,16,Fchallenges including the management of
OL,17,Fan ageing assets... reduction in
OL,18,Fresources including qualified team
OL,19,Fmembers and budgets, challenges
OL,20,Fregarding retention of qualified staff
OL,21,Fand the increased costs.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G4/5
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
